[SHORT DESC]
50% chance to lower target's Special Attack by 1 stage.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage and has a 50% chance to lower the target's Special Attack by one stage.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Mist Ball is a move exclusive to Latias, and while the 50% chance to lower the opponent's Special Attack is useful, the moves Psychic or Psyshock are preferred for their power. Most of Latias's targets are not affected much by a Special Attack drop either, as most of them focus on the defenses.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/psychic">Psychic</a> is a more powerful option.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/psyshock">Psyshock</a> is a more powerful option that hits the opponent's Defense stat.</p>